com.github.lucapino.confluence.model

Class Content

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.lucapino.confluence.model.Content

  • public class Content
extends Object
    Represents a piece of content. Example 
          {
          "id": "22217244",
          "type": "page",
          "space": {
              "key": "TST"
          },
          "title": "A title",
          "body": {
              "storage": {
                  "value": "<p>This is a new page</p>",
                  "representation": "storage"
              }
          }
      }
    Author:
    Jonathon Hope
